name: Chocolate penguin
info: It is a marshmallow penguin drizzled with a lot of chocolate syrup over its head.

name: Straberry penguin
info: It is a marshmallow penguin drizzled with a lot of strawberry syrup over its head.

name: Blueberry penguin
info: Its eyesight is slightly better than other penguins because of blueberry syrup.

name: Banana penguin
info: A banana is originally white, but that doesn’t matter to it.

name: Melon penguin
info: It is an implicit rule to bring a Melon Penguin when you come back.

name: Grape penguin
info: After the day when it ate a lot of grapes, its whole body was covered with purple.

name: Vanila penguin
info: It seems to be expected to have a wonderful nickname, Nilla Nilla Vanilla.

name: Broccoli penguin
info: The fact that broccoli is not only good for your health but also look delicious!

name: Carrot penguin
info: It is sometimes targeted by rabbits because of its fresh carrot color.

name: Eggplant penguin
info: It waits for a day when it can appeal to those who hate eggplant.

name: Mint chocolate penguin
info: It hasn’t washed for a long time, so it became a mushroom. However, it will return to its original state by taking a shower.

name: Watermelon penguin
info: It is a popular costume at Ice Land’s summer festival. Actually, it turns red because it is shy.

name: LEGO penguin
info: It will hurt if you step on it. Another penguin which rides on its top hesitates a little.

name: Milk penguin
info: It doesn’t give up identification as a penguin. It just wants to make the milk-flavored cream stand out.

name: Mushroom penguin
info: Mint syrup is drizzled because of a rumor that everyone like it, but someone doesn’t.

name: Avocado penguin
info: Someday it wants to be nice brunch duo with Salmon Sushi Penguin.

name: Salmon sushi penguin
info: Put the softly melting salmon on its head, dip its beak in wasabi, and then complete the salmon sushi!

name: Earth penguin
info: The earth is round, so if you keep going forward you will arrive at the dessert world.

name: Angel penguin
info: It seems to be kind like an angel, but it is actually very bad.

name: Devil penguin
info: It seems to be bad like a devil, but it is actually very kind.

name: Wizard penguin
info: Sugardium Leviosa. Penguins which want to fly often used to ride a broom.

name: Charlie penguin
info: ….(Quite. It doesn’t answer when somebody talk to it.)

name: Honeybee penguin
info: To harvest honey, it dresses up like a honeybee. Sometimes it dances with swaying its hips.

name: Cherry blossom penguin
info: It feels happy to enjoy a picnic and pick berries at the Ice Cream Hills.

name: Hawaiian penguin
info: After marshmallow penguins clean up, they enjoy taking a break at the Parfait Resort.

name: Librarian penguin
info: When you make a noise in the Cracker Library, somewhere it appears quietly and warn you.

name: Pierrot penguin
info: When a party is held at the Cotton Candy Castle, a clown with cotton candy hair and a berry nose appears.
